 \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanda_Anisimova\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amanda Anisimova\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanda_Anisimova\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanda_Anisimova\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: REUTERS  Published\\u00c2Aug 27, 2024, 10:33 AM  Updated\\u00c2Aug 27, 2024, 09:23 PM  NEW YORK\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093China\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Zheng Qinwen is refusing to let history repeat itself, as she hopes for a deep run at the US Open after claiming her country\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s first Olympic tennis singles gold in Paris.\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 607, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 601, \"end\": 606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999859282981, \"rank\": 1.4071585856782118e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 21-year-old has in the past followed big tournaments with sub-par showings, a fate that she would need to avoid if she wants to win her first Grand Slam.\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 766, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Zheng cleared the first hurdle on Aug 26 as she battled back from a set down to defeat Amanda Anisimova of the United States 4-6, 6-4, 6-2 in New York.\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 768, \"end\": 773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2965596893909906e-19, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}, {\"begin\": 855, \"end\": 871, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanda_Anisimova\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Amanda Anisimova\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanda_Anisimova\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amanda_Anisimova\"}, {\"begin\": 879, \"end\": 892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Davis_Cup_team\", \"score\": 0.9412839955116508, \"rank\": 0.060828150372016186, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Davis_Cup_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Davis_Cup_team\"}, {\"begin\": 910, \"end\": 918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999604103169792, \"rank\": 2.5726212233331187e-05, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the typical match I will lose, especially after huge success, because I know myself.\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Usually after huge success, I will get a little bit too high,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d she said.\", \"from\": 1016, \"to\": 1090, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cSo this time when I get a success, I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m telling myself, I don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t want to let this happen (again).\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m going to continue working hard, keep the stable mindset.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  The Chinese star is no stranger to stumbling soon after soaring in the biggest moments.\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1266, \"end\": 1273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9960209162601897, \"rank\": 0.002444761921614214, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her quarter-final appearance at the 2023 US Open was followed by a first-round exit at the China Open.\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And after reaching the Australian Open final this season, she suffered a sub-par performance at the Qatar Open.\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1565, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After her victory against Anisimova, an on-court interviewer lauded Zheng\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Olympic achievement, but she was quick to say she was looking ahead.\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cTo come to the next tournament (after the Games), everything starts (at) zero.\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1796, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are not any more Olympic champion.\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just be humble and try to work, fight every single match.\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1893, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Because if you don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t fight, you have a big chance you lose,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Zheng added.\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1971, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1959, \"end\": 1964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2965596893909906e-19, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Anisimova had arrived in New York on the upswing.\", \"from\": 1973, \"to\": 2022, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1998, \"end\": 2006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999604103169792, \"rank\": 2.5726212233331187e-05, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was ranked 373rd in the world when she returned from a mental health break in January.\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2113, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But a run to the final at Toronto in August saw her return to the top 50 and gain a wildcard invitation into the main draw at Flushing Meadows.\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2140, \"end\": 2147, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"score\": 0.8416999147332835, \"rank\": 0.1563830834270374, \"text\": \"Toronto\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cEvery ball (from Anisimova) went inside in the beginning and I couldn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t do anything,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Zheng admitted, referring to the first set.\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2395, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2352, \"end\": 2357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2965596893909906e-19, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAs the match goes, I started to find my rhythm... Little by little I started to get into the rhythm.\", \"from\": 2397, \"to\": 2500, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099m really happy to get this match, because she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s really tough to face.\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2580, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like you see, she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s in the final of Toronto.\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2619, \"end\": 2626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"score\": 0.8416999147332835, \"rank\": 0.1563830834270374, \"text\": \"Toronto\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Toronto\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think one of her best surfaces is on hard court.\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cTo (have) won this match means I make one step forward in my mental side.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Zheng will next face Russian Erika Andreeva in the second round.REUTERS, AFP  US Open (Tennis)  Grand Slam  Olympics 2024  China  E-paper  Newsletters  Podcasts  RSS Feed  About Us  Terms & Conditions  Personal Data Protection Notice  Need help?\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 3006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2761, \"end\": 2766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2965596893909906e-19, \"text\": \"Zheng\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zheng_Jie\"}, {\"begin\": 2782, \"end\": 2789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9998991917929343, \"rank\": 9.73409777172158e-05, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2790, \"end\": 2795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erika_Mann\", \"score\": 0.9547485032648019, \"rank\": 0.046608938093069666, \"text\": \"Erika\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erika_Mann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Erika_Mann\"}, {\"begin\": 2796, \"end\": 2804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ekaterina_Andreeva_(arachnologist)\", \"score\": 0.957044069506058, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andreeva\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ekaterina_Andreeva_(arachnologist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc